        "action": "Require 2 forms of identification when voting and stronger scrutinisation ",
        "additional_details": "We think this change could help ensure that voter fraud is minimised and everyone casts their vote legally.                                                                                                                                        ",
        "background": "I want the Ballot Secrecy Act updated, to include 2 tier voter identification system where two types of identification is required per person, and more scrutinisation of Identification by poll station staff.",
